          <description>
            <string language="hu">Az Osztrák-Magyar Monarchia egyesített címere. A szalag felirata: indivisibiliter ac inseparabiliter, feloszthatatlanul és szétválaszthatatlanul.</string>
            <string language="en">the combined coat of arms of the Austro-Hungarian Monarchy. The inscription on the ribbon, indivisibiliter ac inseparabiliter, indivisibility and inseparability</string>

            <string language="hu">dualizmus,  címer,  Pragmatica Sanctio,  kiegyezés,  </string>
            <string language="en">dualism, coat of arms, Pragmatica Sanctio, compromise</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">das kombinierte Wappen der Austro-Ungarischen 
Monarchie. Die Beschreibung auf dem Farbband, 
indivisibiliter Wechselstrom inseparabiliter, Unteilbarkeit und 
Unteilbarkeit</string>
          </description>

Austro-Hongroise. L'inscription sur le ruban, l'inseparabiliter 
à C.A. d'indivisibiliter, l'indivisibilité et l'inséparabilité</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">o revestimento de braços combinado do monarchy 
Austro-austro-Hungarian. O inscription na fita, no 
inseparabiliter da C. A. do indivisibiliter, no indivisibility e no 
inseparability</string>
          </description>

di CA del indivisibiliter, sul indivisibility e sul inseparability</string>
          </description>
          <description>

μοναρχίας. Η επιγραφή στην κορδέλλα, indivisibiliter 
εναλλασσόμενο ρεύμα inseparabiliter, indivisibility και το 
αναπόσπαστο</string>
          </description>

de la CA del indivisibiliter, la indivisibilidad y el inseparability</string>
